                      FTP (File Transfer Protocol) Site

 Welcome! The NGDC Anonymous FTP site allows users to download or contribute
                              geophysical data.
  Data access will generally be easier via the NGDC Data Discipline pages,
          and FTP access is recommended only for experienced users.

     __________________________________________________________________

                               Contribute Data

           Use this location to upload data for the NGDC archive.
             Please also email us when your data is contributed.
     __________________________________________________________________

                                Download Data

    Download Custom Data Files generated for you, or select data from the
           NGDC Anonymous FTP site in the following subject areas:
     __________________________________________________________________

                           Bathymetry & Topography
                                      :

        GLOBE 1Km, 5'Topo, Global Bathy/Topo, Great Lakes, Shorelines

                                Geomagnetism
                                      :

            Aeromag, Main Field, Paleomag, Daily Field Variations

                                   Habitat
                                      :

                    CEOS Data, Ecosystems, Global Change

                                  Hazards:

                Seismicity, Strong Motion, Tsunami, Volcanos

                             Ocean Geosciences:

                Geology, Geophysics, Great Lakes, Shorelines

                                Paleoclimate:

     Coral, Climate Models, Ice Core, Paleocean, Paleolim, Pollen, Tree
                                    Rings

                                 Satellites:

                               DMSP, GOES, SXI

                                   Solar:

         Airglow, Aurorae, Cosmic Rays, Flares, Irradiance, Sunspots

                               Space Weather:

                            Satellite Environment

                                Terrestrial:

                      Geochemistry, Heat Flow, Gravity


    For questions about content please contact: info@ngdc.noaa.gov

                       URL: http://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/ngdcinfo/ngdcftp.html

